1. *Četvrti* put idem u Pariz. (I am going to Paris for the fourth time.)
2. U *četvrtom* mesecu trudnoće osetila sam prve pokrete bebe. (In the fourth month of pregnancy, I felt the baby's first movements.)
3. Prošle nedelje sam kupila *četvrtu* knjigu u serijalu. (Last week I bought the fourth book in the series.)
4. Novac koji smo dobili od prodaje *četvrtine* kuće iskoristili smo za putovanje. (We used the money we got from selling a quarter of the house to travel.)
5. Na *četvrtom* spratu zgrade nalazi se kancelarija koju tražite. (The office you're looking for is on the fourth floor of the building.)
6. Kada se deli sa *četiri*, broj 16 postaje *četiri*. (When divided by four, the number 16 becomes four.)
7. U gradu ima *četiri* pozorišta koja su vredna posete. (There are four theaters in the city that are worth visiting.)
8. *Četvorica* mladića su uhapšena zbog krađe automobila. (Four young men were arrested for stealing a car.)
9. Ovaj kvadrat ima *četiri* jednake strane. (This square has four equal sides.)
10. Na trci su učestvovala *četvorica*, ali samo jedan je pobedio. (Four took part in the race, but only one won.)